data.oai_dc:dc: Plot of Upstream Regulator activation z-scores from the frozen (FR) sample versus Upstream Regulator activation z-scores from the other isolation procedures. Best fit linear regression line is shown and line expression is shown in the upper right side of each panel. Panels are: A) FR versus DP, B) FR versus 18F, C) FR versus DTAE, D) FR versus OH, E) FR versus DQ, F) FR versus 3F, G) FR versus NoD. Abbreviations: FR - frozen, OH - ethanol, 18F – 18hr formalin, 3F - 3m formalin, DTAE - Demod Tris-Acetate EDTA, DQ - Demod 18hr Qiagen, DP - Demod 18hr PureLink, and NoD - Control no catalyst
